---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About TerraTAC">
  <section class="w-full max-w-full mx-auto py-8 px-4 sm:max-w-2xl sm:py-16 sm:px-8 overflow-x-hidden text-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6">About TerraTAC</h1>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg mb-4">TerraTAC is dedicated to providing high-quality tactical and survival gear for professionals and enthusiasts alike. Our mission is to ensure you are always prepared, equipped, and protected, no matter the challenge.</p>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg mb-4">We source only the best products, rigorously tested for reliability and performance. Whether you are in the field, on a mission, or exploring the outdoors, TerraTAC has your back.</p>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg">Thank you for choosing TerraTAC. Stay safe, stay prepared.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
      <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="British Flag" class="h-12 w-12 sm:h-16 sm:w-16" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
